<collectingRegion box="[948,1058,405,431]" country="Japan" name="Hokkaido" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Hokkaido</collectingRegion>
University of Education, who has long contributed to the taxonomy of Asian drosophilids.
</paragraph>
